data.description: Looking for a home perfect for entertaining? Well look no further! Conveniently located near Indian Hills Country Club, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath, brick home features an updated kitchen, complete with granite countertops and stainless appliances, home office which could be utilized as a 4th bedroom, amazing great room, ideal for all your get-togethers, 2 fireplaces, new HVAC, mature trees and so much more!
